{"tid":38954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三人將仿美鈔冥幣存銀行　詐領近6萬落網","createTime":"2016-12-14T09:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T12:58:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"033691c807998570dd47958f579e478f9ae9364d","tid":38954,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkncn-20161214122905605-1214_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161214132545\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161214122905605-1214_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161214132545&h=c9128b03&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四川遂寧市警方近日通報，當地一名李姓男子早前在地攤上購買到仿美鈔冥幣後，轉交給兩名友人，將「面值」9100美元的冥幣存入銀行，再經自動櫃員機（ATM）轉匯提款。事後銀行發現問題，立即打電話報警。目前三人已經落網，並已退還以冥幣兌換的近6萬元人民幣。 <br />\n<br />\n事發於今年7月中旬，其中一名涉事女子拿着面值4600元的「美鈔」，到當地一家銀行在辦理儲蓄業務，由於她當時的存款為外幣，故銀行職員未有詳細驗證，便直接將「美鈔」存款。同日下午，該女子跟另一名男子又拿面值4500元的「美鈔」到銀行存款。兩次存款中，銀行職員都未有發現紙幣有異樣。 <br />\n<br />\n直至當晚，銀行將現金入庫時，銀行負責人檢查外幣時發現當中的「美鈔」竟是冥幣，於是報警求助，警方立即介入調查。 <br />\n<br />\n「這些美元（冥幣）很逼真，但美元背後有一行英文寫上：『錢幣是冥幣，禁止流通交易』。」警員指疑犯將冥幣存入銀行後，便立即透過自動櫃員機轉匯提款。警方透過疑犯的交易紀錄，以及翻查銀行的閉路電視，終抓獲三名疑犯。"},{"pid":"0e59be83f8dd06686a0677f6117287509149dd32","tid":38954,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"兩次存款中，銀行職員都未有發現紙幣有異樣。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c0bb9b45fdbcef633afa75a01f2cbc4c17306410","tid":38954,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"蚹"},{"pid":"ff170188965d7f25f931ee1a8bcf357032a50c53","tid":38954,"uid":37715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"人仔同陰司紙差唔多姐"},{"pid":"35fdd33b5a2e9b4ebda1c15c3b6b2016f9eb4b8f","tid":38954,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6729150d730d9a32ad9c70e1e80c6c12f5d4b89","tid":38954,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9bc4b421826487948950d48a4baba10653b2ba","tid":38954,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"美金=陰司紙<br />\n政冶正確"},{"pid":"2c54d7c7abb8657608f82e3627e08fdb6f7332a3","tid":38954,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"假都可以當真？<br />\n<br />\n銀行都咁撚柒。"},{"pid":"17a852c41e34eb514b66591f7dd92a35601665b8","tid":38954,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩次存款中，銀行職員都未有發現紙幣有異樣。&amp;nbsp;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔出奇邊遠地區d銀行職員好小見到美元"},{"pid":"12943c4c090b5ff949d53eb358e84fe094418011","tid":38954,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"點解張相全部都係 10000 美元嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66af384b9cba30f9eefc3f967dcbd02ae9471bc","tid":38954,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"人蠢無葯醫"},{"pid":"b5312107c1affade981adcc271069a1adba2cb6c","tid":38954,"uid":9258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"其實隨時係同個銀行職員打龍通，係大陸咩都有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63669cf64439a314531555fbe58cc5df80acb7e","tid":38954,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為係支那冥幣<br />\n點知真係冥幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeb7